## Model Configuration

```yaml
agents:
  - id: {{agent_id}}
    name: {{Agent Display Name}}
    model: {{provider/model-name}}  # e.g., openai/gpt-4o
    # Optional: specify thinking level for complex reasoning
    # thinking_level: {{low|medium|high}}
    temperature: {{0.0-1.0}}
    max_tokens: {{integer}}
    
    # Model routing for cost optimization (optional)
    routing:
      enabled: {{true|false}}
      light_model: {{provider/light-model-name}}
      threshold: {{0.0-1.0}}  # Messages scoring below this use light model
    
    # Fallback models if primary fails
    fallbacks:
      - {{fallback_model_1}}
      - {{fallback_model_2}}
    
    # Sub-agent spawning permissions (if this agent can spawn others)
    subagents:
      allow_agents:
        - "*"  # Allow spawning any configured sub-agent
        # Or specify explicitly:
        # - {{subagent_id_1}}
        # - {{subagent_id_2}}
    
    # Skills filter (optional - restrict available skills)
    skills:
      - {{skill_1}}
      - {{skill_2}}
```

